{"tid":2295681,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"藍波撚居然夠膽撩我隻揪","createTime":"2020-11-22T03:40:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T12:23:35.000Z","uid":212639,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ef07eb9423907916fd6786d709ba48fac5316409","tid":2295681,"uid":212639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:40:45.000Z","msg":"小弟今年中五得米7幾 身邊d人個個都米8幾 因為我好細粒 成日比人烚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我而家都的起心肝操大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直到上個星期五 有個籃波撚特登撞鳩我 今次我唔再淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻就打佢一拳 我心諗佢真係唔好彩 我已經操左成四五個月gym 手瓜起晒展 佢哋就喺疫情嗰陣疏於練習 點都係我贏啦 加上起學校球場比小拳石打到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之後一定柒飛起<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我想問邊到有撈麵買？我打輸左 佢要我請食撈麵先肯收手"},{"pid":"6363da990bf52c41d369c05f32406b89f6d76e24","tid":2295681,"uid":363706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87850e28c3b529334f2357b0b96630ef5ae5279c","tid":2295681,"uid":235637,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"巴打 我留意左你好耐<br />\n你真係好幽默<br />\n<br />\n我自問都算個ok幽默既人 但係你幽默感比我真係高十幾二十倍<br />\n<br />\n錯 應該係100倍先岩<br />\n<br />\n估唔到我係呢個post竟然見識到你既威力<br />\n<br />\n我真係笑到爆左肚 依家一路打字一路撿返d腸呀內臟呀腎呀<br />\n<br />\n塞返落個肚到<br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過未來幾個月去紅館開棟篤笑?"},{"pid":"45ab7beba1539845b42c1056867db194cd2888ed","tid":2295681,"uid":212639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"87850e28c3b529334f2357b0b96630ef5ae5279c","tid":2295681,"